```markdown
# Vercel / Local environment variables for api/contact.js

# SendGrid API key (recommended). If set, the function will send emails using SendGrid.
SENDGRID_API_KEY=SG.xxxxxx

# The "from" address used when sending emails. Must be verified in SendGrid.
SENDGRID_FROM=notifications@yourdomain.com

# The destination (recipient) for contact emails.
CONTACT_TO=business@yourdomain.com

# Optional: set a custom port for local dev (used by some local emulators)
PORT=3000
```